quran[31]{c,v,t}:
  79,16,"hyn nadah rabuh balwady almthhar almubarak \"twa\", faqal lh: 'adhhab 'iilaa frewn, 'iinah qad afrt fi alesyan, faqul lh: atwdd 'ana tthhir nafsak min alnqays wthlyha bal'iyman, w'urshdk 'iilaa taeat rbk, ftkhshah wttqyh?"
  79,17,"hyn nadah rabuh balwady almthhar almubarak \"twa\", faqal lh: 'adhhab 'iilaa frewn, 'iinah qad afrt fi alesyan, faqul lh: atwdd 'ana tthhir nafsak min alnqays wthlyha bal'iyman, w'urshdk 'iilaa taeat rbk, ftkhshah wttqyh?"
  79,18,"hyn nadah rabuh balwady almthhar almubarak \"twa\", faqal lh: 'adhhab 'iilaa frewn, 'iinah qad afrt fi alesyan, faqul lh: atwdd 'ana tthhir nafsak min alnqays wthlyha bal'iyman, w'urshdk 'iilaa taeat rbk, ftkhshah wttqyh?"
  79,19,"hyn nadah rabuh balwady almthhar almubarak \"twa\", faqal lh: 'adhhab 'iilaa frewn, 'iinah qad afrt fi alesyan, faqul lh: atwdd 'ana tthhir nafsak min alnqays wthlyha bal'iyman, w'urshdk 'iilaa taeat rbk, ftkhshah wttqyh?"
  79,20,"fara musaa frewn aleallamat alezma: aleasa walyd, fakadhab fireawn nby allah musaa ealayh alslam, wesa rabih ezz wjlla, thuma wlla merdana ean al'iiman mjthdana fi muearadat mwsa"
  79,21,"fara musaa frewn aleallamat alezma: aleasa walyd, fakadhab fireawn nby allah musaa ealayh alslam, wesa rabih ezz wjlla, thuma wlla merdana ean al'iiman mjthdana fi muearadat mwsa"
  79,22,"fara musaa frewn aleallamat alezma: aleasa walyd, fakadhab fireawn nby allah musaa ealayh alslam, wesa rabih ezz wjlla, thuma wlla merdana ean al'iiman mjthdana fi muearadat mwsa"
  79,23,"fjme 'ahl mmlkth wnadahm, fqal: 'ana rabukum aldhy la rbb fwqh, fantqm allah minh bialeadhab fi aldunya walakhrt, wjelh eibratan wnkala lamthalh min almtmrdyn. 'iina fi fireawn wama nazal bih min aleadhab lmweztan liman ytez wynzjr"
  79,24,"fjme 'ahl mmlkth wnadahm, fqal: 'ana rabukum aldhy la rbb fwqh, fantqm allah minh bialeadhab fi aldunya walakhrt, wjelh eibratan wnkala lamthalh min almtmrdyn. 'iina fi fireawn wama nazal bih min aleadhab lmweztan liman ytez wynzjr"
  79,25,"fjme 'ahl mmlkth wnadahm, fqal: 'ana rabukum aldhy la rbb fwqh, fantqm allah minh bialeadhab fi aldunya walakhrt, wjelh eibratan wnkala lamthalh min almtmrdyn. 'iina fi fireawn wama nazal bih min aleadhab lmweztan liman ytez wynzjr"
  79,26,"fjme 'ahl mmlkth wnadahm, fqal: 'ana rabukum aldhy la rbb fwqh, fantqm allah minh bialeadhab fi aldunya walakhrt, wjelh eibratan wnkala lamthalh min almtmrdyn. 'iina fi fireawn wama nazal bih min aleadhab lmweztan liman ytez wynzjr"
  79,27,"abaethukm 'ayuha alnas- baed almawt 'ashadu fi tqdyrkm 'am khalaq alsma'? rafaeaha fawqakum kalbna', waela sqfha fi alhawa' la tafawut fiha wala ftwr, wazlm laylaha bghrwb shmsha, wa'abraz nharha bshrwqha. wal'ard baed khalaq alsama' bstha, wawde fiha mnafeha, wfjjar fiha euyun alma', wanbt fiha ma yurea min alnbatat, wathbt fiha aljibal awtadana lha. khalaq subhanah kl hadhih alnaeam manfaeat lakum wlaneamkm. ('in 'iieadat khalaqakum yawm alqiamat 'ahwan ealaa allah min khalq hadhih alashya', wklh ealaa allah hayin ysyr)"
  79,28,"abaethukm 'ayuha alnas- baed almawt 'ashadu fi tqdyrkm 'am khalaq alsma'? rafaeaha fawqakum kalbna', waela sqfha fi alhawa' la tafawut fiha wala ftwr, wazlm laylaha bghrwb shmsha, wa'abraz nharha bshrwqha. wal'ard baed khalaq alsama' bstha, wawde fiha mnafeha, wfjjar fiha euyun alma', wanbt fiha ma yurea min alnbatat, wathbt fiha aljibal awtadana lha. khalaq subhanah kl hadhih alnaeam manfaeat lakum wlaneamkm. ('in 'iieadat khalaqakum yawm alqiamat 'ahwan ealaa allah min khalq hadhih alashya', wklh ealaa allah hayin ysyr)"
