  79,33,"abaethukm 'ayuha alnas- baed almawt 'ashadu fi tqdyrkm 'am khalaq alsma'? rafaeaha fawqakum kalbna', waela sqfha fi alhawa' la tafawut fiha wala ftwr, wazlm laylaha bghrwb shmsha, wa'abraz nharha bshrwqha. wal'ard baed khalaq alsama' bstha, wawde fiha mnafeha, wfjjar fiha euyun alma', wanbt fiha ma yurea min alnbatat, wathbt fiha aljibal awtadana lha. khalaq subhanah kl hadhih alnaeam manfaeat lakum wlaneamkm. ('in 'iieadat khalaqakum yawm alqiamat 'ahwan ealaa allah min khalq hadhih alashya', wklh ealaa allah hayin ysyr)"
  79,34,"f'idha ja'at alqiamat alkubraa walshidat aleuzmaa wahi alnfkht althanyt, endydh yuerad ealaa al'iinsan kl eamalih min khayr wshr, fytdhkrh wyetrf bh, w'uzhrt jahanam likuli mubsir tura eianana"
  79,35,"f'idha ja'at alqiamat alkubraa walshidat aleuzmaa wahi alnfkht althanyt, endydh yuerad ealaa al'iinsan kl eamalih min khayr wshr, fytdhkrh wyetrf bh, w'uzhrt jahanam likuli mubsir tura eianana"
  79,36,"f'idha ja'at alqiamat alkubraa walshidat aleuzmaa wahi alnfkht althanyt, endydh yuerad ealaa al'iinsan kl eamalih min khayr wshr, fytdhkrh wyetrf bh, w'uzhrt jahanam likuli mubsir tura eianana"
  79,37,"famma man tamarud ealaa 'amr allh, wafadl alhayat aldunya ealaa alakhrt, fa'iina masirih 'iilaa alnar"
  79,38,"famma man tamarud ealaa 'amr allh, wafadl alhayat aldunya ealaa alakhrt, fa'iina masirih 'iilaa alnar"
  79,39,"famma man tamarud ealaa 'amr allh, wafadl alhayat aldunya ealaa alakhrt, fa'iina masirih 'iilaa alnar"
  79,40,"wamma man khaf alqiam bayn yaday allah llhsab, wanahaa alnafs ean alahwa' alfasdt, fa'iina aljanat hi msknh"
  79,41,"wamma man khaf alqiam bayn yaday allah llhsab, wanahaa alnafs ean alahwa' alfasdt, fa'iina aljanat hi msknh"
  79,42,"yas'aluk almushrikun 'ayuha alrswl- astkhfafa- ean waqt hulul alssaeat alty ttwedhm bha. lst fi shay' min elmha, bal marada dhlk 'iilaa allah eaza wjl, wa'iinama shank fi 'amr alsaaeat 'ana thdhr minha man ykhafha. ka'anahum yawm yarawn qiam alssaeat lam yalbathuu fi alhayat aldnya; lhwl alsaaeat 'iilaa ma bayn alzuhr 'iilaa ghrwb alshms, 'aw ma bayn tulue alshams 'iilaa nsf alnhar"
  79,43,"ysalk almushrikun 'ayuha alrswl- astkhfafa- ean waqt hulul alssaeat alty ttwedhm bha. lst fi shay' min elmha, bal marada dhlk 'iilaa allah eaza wjl, wa'iinama shank fi 'amr alsaaeat 'ana thdhr minha man ykhafha. ka'anahum yawm yarawn qiam alssaeat lam yalbathuu fi alhayat aldnya; lhwl alsaaeat 'iilaa ma bayn alzuhr 'iilaa ghrwb alshms, 'aw ma bayn tulue alshams 'iilaa nsf alnhar"
